    <h3>
      <span class="headline__main" data-js-select="Headline_main">
        <span>
          Selecting an OCT for your service
        </span>
        
      </span>
      
    </h3>
    
    
  </div>



    

</div>


      
      <div class="text text--body-m">
    <p>Optical Coherence Tomography (OCT) is becoming increasingly important in the early detection and management of diabetic eye diseases.</p>
<p><b>That’s why you need an OCT that can seamlessly integrate into your screening workflow and enhance patient care.</b></p>
<p>As the world’s leading innovator in OCT, and years of collaboration with clinicians around the world, at ZEISS we understand the clinical challenges you face - and the importance of optimising the user and patient experience…</p>




    

</div>


      
      <div class="text-media-item-horizontal__link">
        
        
      </div>
